						<summary>

						<p>This is a damaged epigraph recording a gift of gold for a perpetual lamp in the temple of Gōvindapāḍi-Āḷvār by one Nārāyaṇa-Kramavittan <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Vaidumbarāditya-Brahmādhirājaṉ of Ikkāṭṭukkōṭṭam, who deposited the amount with the <hi rend="italic">sabhā</hi> of Vallam in Dāmarkōṭṭam for the necessary supply of oil for the purpose, by the liquid measure <hi rend="italic">Ūragattuniṉṟār-kāl.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
